    <description><![CDATA[
# clob — Universal AI in your terminal

clob is an open-source universal AI terminal platform with a modern TUI.

## Features

- **Modern TUI** — Full Textual-powered terminal interface with sidebar, streaming chat, markdown rendering
- **Multiple providers** — OpenRouter, Groq, NVIDIA Build, Ollama (local), any OpenAI-compatible API
- **Real-time streaming** — Token-by-token response rendering
- **Persistent memory** — SQLite-backed session and chat history
- **Workspace context** — Inject files and directories into AI prompts with @file, @dir
- **Analytics** — Track token usage and estimated cost
- **Themes** — dark, light, cyberpunk, nord and custom themes
- **Plugin system** — Extend with custom providers, tools, and agents

## Quick Start

```
# Set your API key
setx OPENROUTER_API_KEY "your-key-here"

# Launch TUI
clob

# Or send a message
clob chat "Hello!"
```

## Configuration

Config file: `%USERPROFILE%\.config\clob\config.toml`

## Documentation

Full documentation: https://github.com/crishacks/clob
